lead_paragraph: Beleaguered manager Roberto Martinez insisted his Everton players have full confidence in him and he does not see the need to regain their trust following Saturday's timid 3-1 Premier League loss to champions Leicester City.

headline.print_headline: Martinez Sees No Need to Win Back Everton Players
headline.main: Martinez Sees No Need to Win Back Everton Players
